      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cod-cli-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
