           move      40                   to   v-car                  .
           move      16                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      41                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-rig-cod-cli-rag    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-cod-cli-rag-999.
